<!-- Certified Dealer Benefits -->
<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header centered">
            <span class="section-eyebrow">Why Buy from a Certified Dealer</span>
            <h2>Local Expertise. Factory-Backed Products.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="three-col-grid">
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">🎓</div>
                <h3>Factory-Trained Specialists</h3>
                <p>Every DripSmart certified dealer completes our training program and earns annual recertification. They know our product line better than anyone and how it performs in your local conditions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">📐</div>
                <h3>Expert System Design</h3>
                <p>Certified dealers provide hydraulic design, layout, and product specification for your project — so your system is sized and configured correctly the first time.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">🚚</div>
                <h3>Fast Local Delivery</h3>
                <p>Stocking dealers keep the most popular DripSmart products on-hand for same or next-day delivery — so you're not waiting weeks when the season is on.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">🔧</div>
                <h3>Installation &amp; Service</h3>
                <p>Most certified dealers offer professional installation, start-up commissioning, and ongoing maintenance — full turnkey service from a local partner who knows your farm.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">🤝</div>
                <h3>Warranty &amp; Support</h3>
                <p>Purchases through certified dealers include full DripSmart factory warranty coverage and direct access to our technical support team when you need it.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">💳</div>
                <h3>Financing Available</h3>
                <p>Many dealers offer DripSmart-backed financing programs — including 0% interest for 12 months on qualifying system purchases. Ask your dealer about current programs.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<div class="callout-mustard">
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Can't Find a Dealer Near You?</h2>
        <p>Contact us directly — our team will connect you with the nearest certified partner or ship directly to your location.</p>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Contact DripSmart Directly</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
